                            · Venue: Auxenta Head Office 
                            ( No 61, 3rd Floor, Janadhipathi Mawatha, Colombo 01 )
                        </pre>
                      <p
                        style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        Google Map Reference : <a
                          href="https://www.google.lk/maps/place/Carson+Cumberbatch+PLC/@6.9345482,79.8423443,17z/data=!4m8!1m2!2m1!1s61+janadhipathi+mawatha+colombo+1!3m4!1s0x3ae25925b821e043:0xde32ff9241921f5a!8m2!3d6.9336291!4d79.8429445?hl=en">Auxenta
                          Head Office</a>
                      </p>
                      <p
