                      <p
                        style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        <b>Thanks and Best Regards, </b></p>
                      <p
                        style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; Margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        {{hrperson}} | Human Resources <br />
                        Auxenta (Pvt) Ltd | Colombo <br />
                        <img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/987193092145950720/qEQhRm98_400x400.jpg"
                          style="width:100px;height:100px;vertical-align:middle" alt="auxentaLogo">
                      </p>

                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>

